Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoshi no Kotodama
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my dreams, I will embrace,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}anata e no omoi dake o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just my feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yume ni dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very slowly, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yukkuri to watashi wa ima
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I am starting to take an adult form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ah otona no kakera ni kawaru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Ah, you're here.\NAh, I am starting to take an adult form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The love I hold in my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yume ni aru aiji dake ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes. I'm sorry I couldn't help you.\NThe love I hold in my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes. I'm sorry I couldn't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes. I'm sorry I couldn't help you.\Nshines brighter than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}nani yori mo kagayaite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shines brighter than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Oh, don't worry. That's no problem.\Nshines brighter than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shines brighter than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– The dream you wanted to accomplish before you died:\Nshines brighter than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– The dream you wanted to accomplish before you died:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}oh kui ga nai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– a field of cosmos flowers overlooking the sea.\NOh, I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was able to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:01:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}mata anata ni deaete watashi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– If there's anything I can do to make\Nyour dream come true, I'll try.\NBecause I was able to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was able to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}shiawase datta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I'm sorry.\NAnd I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Uh, well...\NAnd I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I guess I need more training.\NAnd I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 2:\NReturn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's colder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd see the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you'd work so hard at something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yoshihira. What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, don't be rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the cosmos flowers from\Nthe gardening club at school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and brought them here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandpa said you'd be here, of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it. Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll plant them soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So have you quit school and run away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or have you decided to become a florist?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll introduce you to my grandmother,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she can teach you flower arrang
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.\Nand she can teach you flower arrang
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, whoa, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. I don't have time to waste here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta go back to school. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt he'd believe me if I told him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin pyo to sha kai jin retsu zai zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I felt something strange.\NI must've imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin pyo to sha kai jin retsu zai zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin pyo to sha kai jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flower garden will be finished soon, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By next fall, this field will be\Ncovered in cosmos flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do now is plant the\Nseeds Yoshihira brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when that happens, Shigemaro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! Did I get your hand dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel the warmth of your hand very clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess my training paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Training?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. My grandpa told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to do a bunch of spiritual exercises\Nbefore coming here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa says my gift alone\Nisn't enough to help ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to train hard every day and work\Nhard to make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I won't even be able to see you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you finish this flower garden,\NI won't see you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What's been holding you back\Nfrom passing on will be a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My real dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to plant a cosmos flower\Ngarden with the man I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very beautiful Kiyomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... What is this feeling? I've never felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already so wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spread your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go through with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... hurt me. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready? I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time. Don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... a miracle!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cosmos flowers are in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyomi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you moping around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you training, my boy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddaya mean, "Oh, it's just Grandpa"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I explained to you earlier, a beginner like you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must train hard every day to be able\Nto communicate with ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must protect them and yourself\Nfrom evil spirits and monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you expect to help them reincarnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's lovesick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you. I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? I don't really believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he might be telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, that place has been\Nknown as a haunt for ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really scared me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just after I came out of a tunnel,\Nthis spirit-orb thingie came like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just Shigemaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that. I almost had a heart attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshihira! You just mentioned a tunnel, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that tunnel just above the waterfall\Nwhere you were chanting earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to morning practice with my club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right Shigcmaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This morning{\i0}...\NHaven't you been around there a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you been around there a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost. It's kinda bluish-white.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking your bike for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyomi-chan, you must've returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Kiyomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was, all excited that I finally\Nfound someone who could see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki Kaoru. And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koga Shigemaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're creeping me out. Stop staring at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I just had a hard time looking at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I'm hard on your eyes!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! I mean that you're difficult to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense an evil presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when I tried to grab my cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost control of your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I was dying, I kept wondering who was calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not like it matters now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lose it during the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If was difficult for me to drive with it on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I always kept it on the dashboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ring was important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's pinky swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably because you're so optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even feel dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. I guess I need more training.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, that's okay. I just hope you find my ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will. You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of that thing that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn monster! Let me show you something I learned!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, chains that bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chain binding charm didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What kind of monster is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guide of the Dead, Karasutengu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasutengu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's {\i1}you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah, it's you"? Show some respect why don't'cha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just used his wind barrier to block that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can usually be countered with basic magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you want to actually defeat him,\Nyou'll need some Chobuku magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind barrier? Chobuku... magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! That's the bike I borrowed from Yoshihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's the least of your troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin pyo to sha kai jin retsu zai zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? It didn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. Grandpa said it would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head for the tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You ve got spells on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad enough your grandpa summoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he put these stupid papers on my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grandpa said I should talk to you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you were able to appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Why are you humans so forceful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gonna leave a scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told me about this at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle will be decided by one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what your grandpa said. I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobuku magic... a trapping spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I lured him into the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle will be decided by\None blow, so make if count.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.24,0:20:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make my training count.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin pyo to sha kai jin retsu zai zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin pyo to sha kai jin retsu zai zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But throw it away, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I got dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was a little out of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't care what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy you found it for me, but I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's what she wants, it's what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I never did get the hang of\Nunderstanding a woman's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that girl looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was holding on this whole time, but I finally gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I thought it was okay if I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I wish I were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead. Throw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw it as far into the ocean as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That little devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cosmos Hospital"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's the hospital Aki-chan was going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sakaki Kaoru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:24:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaoru-chan... She was in a coma here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She wasn't really dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.47,0:24:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this point on, it all depends on\Nyour training and your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I guess I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.90,0:24:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her spirit still hasn't completely returned to her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.57,0:24:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.37,0:25:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigemaro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.14,0:25:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.94,0:25:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.88,0:25:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're still not...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.11,0:25:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was dreaming the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.28,0:25:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I kept wishing I were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.49,0:25:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I met you, I wanted to live again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.29,0:25:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted it from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.62,0:26:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.73,0:26:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take off your pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.80,0:26:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.70,0:26:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.66,0:26:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.40,0:26:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.52,0:27:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.09,0:27:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.66,0:27:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.02,0:27:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.16,0:27:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.54,0:27:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.91,0:28:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.90,0:28:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instant I open my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.90,0:28:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}me o aketa shunkan ni
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.14,0:28:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness flees from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.14,0:28:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}shiawase wa nigeteku kara
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.74,0:28:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to stay this way forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.74,0:28:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}eien ni kono mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.08,0:28:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.08,0:28:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}me o tojite itai
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.16,0:28:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I am in your arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.16,0:28:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ima anata no ude no naka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.50,0:29:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embraced gently,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.50,0:29:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yasashiku dakarete
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.20,0:29:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I am changing into an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.20,0:29:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}sou watashi wa maboroshi ni kawaru keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.05,0:29:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't let it fade away,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.05,0:29:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}douka kesanai de
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.49,0:29:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The love that remains in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.49,0:29:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}mune ni tomaru ai o
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.00,0:29:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, someday in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.00,0:29:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kitto mirai demo
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.87,0:29:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, and only I, will be yours forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.87,0:29:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}watashi dake ga your forever